<HEADLINE> College Does Room Service for Free  </HEADLINE>
By JIM FITZGERALD, Associated Press Writer
<TEXT>
<P>
   PURCHASE, N.Y. (AP) -- Tara Eliason was hungry but didn't want to
leave her dorm. It was noon on the day before spring break at
