</P>
<P>
   1956 -- ''Around the World in 80 Days,'' 5.
</P>
<P>
   1957 -- ''The Bridge on the River Kwai,'' 7.
</P>
<P>
   1958 -- ''Gigi,'' 9.
</P>
<P>
   1959 -- ''Ben-Hur,'' 11.
