</P>
<P>
   At Tucson, Larry Walker and Terry Shumpert each hit solo homers.
Troy Glaus and Scott Spiezio drove in Anaheim's runs, and Darin
Erstad had two singles to extend his hitting streak to 15 games.
Brewers 9, Athletics (ss) 2:
</P>
